<!-- 1.5.3 -->
<div class='toload lemma'>
<p><span class='envidentifier'>Lemma 1.5.3</span>
If $S$ is a $\lor$-ideal of a distributive inverse semigroup $S$, then</p>
<ol class='alphpar'>
	<li> If $S$ has a zero then $0\in I$.</li>
	<li> $i\in I$ if and only if $i^*\in I$.</li>
	<li> If $i\in I$ and $j\leq i$ then $j\in I$.</li>
	<li> $a\sim_I b$ if and only if $a^*\sim_I b^*$.</li>
	<li> If $a=b\lor i$ and $i\in I$ then $a\sim_I b$.</li>
</ol>
</div>